[chattering]

01:23.333 --> 01:26.127
[man speaking indistinctly over radio]

01:28.338 --> 01:29.172
[thunder rumbling]

01:36.304 --> 01:37.472
I wanna make a toast...

01:38.473 --> 01:39.766
to the love of my life.

01:41.601 --> 01:43.353
Belle, I wanna tell you something.

01:44.395 --> 01:47.982
I have never been as happy
as I am right now.

01:48.566 --> 01:50.026
